            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>chopped onion</strong> and <strong>chopped pepper</strong> to the pan with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and cook for 7-8 min or until the vegetables have softened</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
